{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it illegal to sell a drone without including a copy of the Drone Code",
        "additional_details": "Illegal drone use is a major problem and when caught, some  operators claim ignorance of the rules. If every drone sold had a copy of the drone code with it then there could be no defence",
        "background": "Both retail and private sales of drones should include, by law, a copy of the Drone Code, UK drone regulations.",
